{"tid":599891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係英國working holiday 吹兩句","createTime":"2018-03-21T00:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T18:38:15.000Z","uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3f12ac587a3bb6bb80d76924a72a6dcd1419d9","tid":599891,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:37:06.000Z","msg":"大學就grad business second upper<br />\n唔想留係香港 想出去睇下個世界 對英國有情意結 英文聽說讀寫都流利 岩岩補領左bno 好想襯後生出去睇下個世界 <br />\n<br />\n想知有無巴絲打係英國做緊嘢 <br />\n可唔可以講下做緊咩 做左幾耐 係邊到做<br />\n同埋要預幾多錢左右 用左幾耐搵工<br />\n透過咩渠道搵工 人工幾多 有咩要求<br />\n<br />\n有無咩工種需要香港人 除左London服待同胞<br />\n<br />\n我聽人講有法例要先請英國公民 之後EU <br />\n先到其他國籍 以保障失業率<br />\n脫左歐會唔會好啲<br />\n<br />\n自己好想做office工 打下雜學下嘢都好<br />\n最理想係做下銀行 不過好似好難搵 <br />\n因為老闆見你working holiday都唔係好想請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人搵獵頭公司 聽講食水好深<br />\n<br />\n如果要做餐廳 或者做sales 我就算<br />\n唔想嘥時間用係呢啲工上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有啲迷茫<br />\n感謝各位大大。"},{"pid":"550b7cf4d14e73a2e72385d74b83a6226860a502","tid":599891,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"Rush"},{"pid":"d0289b89ff84ad908d0760e5b9884eb1e5af3ea0","tid":599891,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:15:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c044f6b224629de104cb733633100e0bbad4b4bc","tid":599891,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係諗住去英國<br />\n又係今年fg <br />\n都好驚去到搵唔到工<br />\n由其係香港都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋零工作經驗好似幾難搞<br />\n英國佬好睇經驗"},{"pid":"3f4c1f419aace0b19d21c2d3452dfc97d1377c57","tid":599891,"uid":155554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T23:39:31.000